<div class="header">
<h1>Aim & Scope</h1>
</div>

<div class="container">

<h2>Aim</h2>

<p>
The International Journal of Pharmacology Research (IJPR) aims to promote
high-quality research and scientific advancement in pharmacology,
pharmaceutical sciences, biotechnology, and healthcare research.
</p>

<h2>Scope</h2>

<ul>
<li>Experimental Pharmacology</li>
<li>Clinical Pharmacology</li>
<li>Pharmacovigilance</li>
<li>Drug Discovery & Development</li>
<li>Molecular Pharmacology</li>
<li>Toxicology</li>
<li>Clinical Pharmacy</li>
<li>Pharmaceutical Chemistry</li>
<li>Pharmaceutics</li>
<li>Pharmacognosy</li>
<li>Nanomedicine</li>
<li>Biotechnology</li>
<li>Artificial Intelligence in Healthcare</li>
<li>Personalized Medicine</li>
<li>Public Health Research</li>
<li>Regulatory Affairs</li>
</ul>

</div>

